Read the repository root `SKILL.md` before performing Planetable API work. Use `references/api.md` for endpoint details and `scripts/planetable.py` for sanitized probes and common operations.

Default to loopback discovery (`127.0.0.1:9191`, then `127.0.0.1:8086`) unless `PLANETABLE_BASE_URL` or the user provides a base URL. Treat `GET /v0/planets/my` as sensitive and do not expose tokens, keys, custom code, SSH/rsync fields, or provider configuration in chat.
